source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04301_000010_BAGGAMONAN<tab>Long have I waited for this moment, Garlean swine!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04301_000010_BAGGAMONAN<tab>J'attends cet instant depuis si longtemps, porcs de Garlemaldais<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04301_000011_BAGGAMONAN<tab>Come! The blood of my fallen brothers feeds my hate!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04301_000011_BAGGAMONAN<tab>Approchez<var 1D /var>! Vous allez payer pour le sang de mes frères<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04301_000020_BAGGAMONAN<tab>You may have escaped me in this life, but I...I shall be waiting in the next!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04301_000020_BAGGAMONAN<tab>Si je n'ai pas eu ma vengeance... dans cette vie... je l'aurai dans la suivante<var 1D /var>!
